data.description: Welcome to your new home! This move-in  ready 3Br. 2 bath  brick home in North Columbus situated on a large , beautiful lot is waiting for you! Tastefully decorated with oodles of storage space. 5 year old roof, new water heater and renovated in 2019. Walk into the huge open Great room in this easy flowing floor plan. W/ breakfast area Kitchen with SS appliances and beautifully decorated finishes. Formal dining room. Laundry room with cabinets and a bright cheery Sunroom. Master bedroom with large walk-in closet . Carport w/ add. parking pad. Wired Outbuilding/ and additional large enclosed storage area and Fenced back yard. This won't last long!!
